<div class="block-player-info">
    <h4>Biography</h4>
    <!-- Quote Modern-->
    <article class="quote-modern">
        <div class="quote-modern-text">
            <p>Jack Windsor is the best player in our team. Technically perfect, he brings together unselfishness, pace,
                composure and goals, which make him number one.</p>
        </div>
